<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad">
  <body>
    <div metal:fill-slot="main">
      <div>
        <a href="/+groups">Translation groups</a>
      </div>
      <h1>
        <tal:translation-group replace="context/title">
          Foo bar
        </tal:translation-group> translation group
      </h1>

      <p class="documentDescription" tal:content="context/summary">
        $TranslationGroup.summary goes here. This should be quite short,
        just a single paragraph of text really, giving a summary of
        this TranslationGroup.
      </p>
      <p>
        Group owner:
        <a tal:content="context/owner/displayname"
           tal:attributes="href context/owner/fmt:url"
           class="link" />
        <a tal:condition="context/required:launchpad.Edit" href="+reassign">
          <img src="/@@/edit" alt="Reassign" title="Change Owner" />
        </a>
      </p>

      <div class="left">
        <div class="section">
          <div class="portlet">
            <h2>Translation Teams</h2>
            <tal:translators condition="context/translators">
              <table class="sortable listing" id="group-members">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Language</th>
                    <th>Translator</th>
                    <th></th>
                    <th>Appointed</th>
                    <th tal:condition="context/required:launchpad.Edit"></th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr tal:repeat="translator view/translator_list">
                    <td tal:content="translator/lang" />
                    <td><a tal:content="translator/person/browsername"
                            tal:attributes="href translator/person/fmt:url" />
                    </td>
                    <td><a tal:attributes="href translator/code"><img
                           src="/@@/edit" alt="Change"
                           title="Change Translator" /></a>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      <span class="sortkey"
                        tal:content="translator/datecreated/fmt:datetime" />
                      <span
                        tal:attributes="title translator/datecreated/fmt:datetime"
                        tal:content="translator/datecreated/fmt:approximatedate">
                        2007-09-17
                      </span>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                      <a
                        tal:attributes="href string:${translator/code}/+remove">
                        <input type="image" style="border: 0;"
                               src="/@@/remove" alt="Remove Translator"
                               title="Remove Translator" name="rmform" />
                      </a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </tal:translators>
            <tal:no-translators condition="not: context/translators">
              There are no translators appointed in this group yet.
            </tal:no-translators>
            <ul class="menu">
              <tal:can-edit condition="context/required:launchpad.Edit">
                <li class="add">
                  <a href="+appoint">Appoint additional translators</a>
                </li>
                <li class="edit">
                  <a href="+edit">Edit translation group details</a>
                </li>
              </tal:can-edit>
              <tal:cannot-edit
                condition="not:context/required:launchpad.Edit">
                <li class="locked">
                  <a href="+appoint">Appoint additional translators</a>
                </li>
                <li class="locked">
                  <a href="+edit">Edit translation group details</a>
                </li>
              </tal:cannot-edit>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <div class="section">
          <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-relateds" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div metal:fill-slot="help">
      <p>
        This is an overview of the
        "<span tal:replace="context/name">transgroup</span>" translation
        group.  A translation group
        is a collection of people who work together on translating software.
        A translation group can translate any number of projects into any
        number of languages.  Translation groups make it easier to coordinate
        and oversee large translation efforts.
      </p>
      <p>
        Within the group, a translator is appointed for every language that the
        group supports.  The translator may be a person or a team.  A person
        or team may work on multiple languages if desired, and even participate
        in multiple translation groups.
      </p>
      <ul class="info">
        <li>
          <a href="https://help.launchpad.net/RosettaFAQ"
          >Frequently asked questions</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
